# .copilot
project_title: AHEAD Official Website Deployment
project_type: Next.js + Caddy + Docker Compose
primary_language: TypeScript
secondary_languages: JavaScript, Shell, Makefile
frameworks: Next.js, TailwindCSS, Radix UI
infrastructure: Docker, Docker Compose, Caddy, Trivy
ci_cd: Makefile-based automation, Git pull deploy, vulnerability scan

## Coding Style
- Use TypeScript for all new code and prefer type safety.
- Use functional React components and hooks.
- Use TailwindCSS for styling, avoid inline styles.
- Use Prettier and ESLint for code formatting and linting.
- Use async/await for asynchronous code.
- Use environment variables for configuration.
- Use descriptive variable and function names in English.

